<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE MOST PRECIOUS NAME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hungun, Minlun lampak hitiu,
 I Hukdampau, Tanpau Lalpen chuh;
 A hehpihna hing I lunggil un,
 Kumsawt in chawian zing hitiu.

[V2]
 Min lulpen, Hukdampa,
 A lopi lam bang pak hitiu;
 Min lulpen, Hukdampa, Hukdampa,
 Lalpa chu lam bang pak hitiu.

[V3]
 2. A hehpihna lopi ziek chun,
 I sapnau cheng silhpuon bang ei khuh;
 Buoina nasa leh lungdawnna ah,
 Hukdampa'n eipui zel ina.

[V4]
 3. Thagau in ei hihhalh nadi'n,
 Pathien in phungbang eivuk intin;
 Kuole A min thiengtho samta chuh,
 Hukdampa'n hukhing zel ina.

[V5]
 4. Hungun, Minlun lampak hitiu,
 I Hukdampau Tanpau Lalpen chuh;
 A lopi zie leh A thientho zie,
 I lunggil ah daibang cha'm hen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>98</hymn_number>
</song>